character_name: James Darrell Edwards III / Agent J: Still on active duty with the MIB
Kevin Brown / Agent K: A decommissioned senior MIB agent and the only person who used to know how to stop the latest threat to Earth's safety.
Serleena: A shapeshifting alien who has come to Earth to find a vital power source used by her race's enemies.
Laura Vasquez: A young woman who turns out to be the long-lost alien princess from Zartha and the power source sought by Serleena.
Jack Jeebs: An alien pawn shop owner who uses a home-built machine to "de-neuralize" K and restore his memory.
Chief Zed: The head of the MIB.
